    <item>
      <title>赞比亚关闭与刚果的边境，阻断关键铜贸易路线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/zambia-closes-border-with-congo-blocking-key-copper-trade-route</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚政府周末表示，已暂时关闭与刚果民主共和国的边境，此举可能会导致非洲最大铜生产国的出口延迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/zambia-closes-border-with-congo-blocking-key-copper-trade-route</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 13:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强基础设施防御以应对伊朗袭击风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/israel-bolsters-infrastructure-defense-amid-iranian-attack-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果人们需要进入避难所，市长们准备好了电池供电的警报器，急救人员准备好了卫星电话和老式晶体管收音机，它们可以成为信息生命线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/israel-bolsters-infrastructure-defense-amid-iranian-attack-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 13:37:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员押注 CPI 数据将大幅波动，以测试市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/traders-bet-on-wild-swings-with-cpi-print-set-to-test-the-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街令人难忘的夏天即将到来，所有人的目光都集中在本周的消费者价格报告上，交易员们希望该报告将为美联储在 9 月份下次会议上开始降息提供所需的弹药。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/traders-bet-on-wild-swings-with-cpi-print-set-to-test-the-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 13:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特改革投资法以吸引外国人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/saudis-reform-investment-law-in-bid-to-draw-in-more-foreigners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯宣布了新的商业法规，旨在提高透明度并简化投资流程，以吸引更多外国资本来支持经济多元化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/saudis-reform-investment-law-in-bid-to-draw-in-more-foreigners</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 10:48:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金属价格飙升后奥运金牌价值比以往任何时候都高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/olympic-gold-medals-are-worth-more-than-ever</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年巴黎奥运会的金牌价值比以往任何时候都高，每枚金牌的原材料价值可能达到 900 美元左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/olympic-gold-medals-are-worth-more-than-ever</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 10:32:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
